Minimum lot size:

llm_output.rationale: The section titled 'MANUFACTURED HOME RESIDENTIAL DISTRICT' provides the minimum lot size for the MH (Manufactured Home) zone. It specifies two different sizes based on the availability of public or community water and sewage disposal systems.
llm_output.answer: 20,000 sq ft; 10,000 sq ft if served by approved public or community water and sewage disposal system
